review:
Outstanding Dental Experience**

I had an amazing experience with Doctor Praveen kumar sir. They were friendly and the clinic environment was great. The receptionist and everyone there were incredibly hospitable. No unnecessary procedures were suggested, and the wisdom tooth removal and filling for my hard-to-reach upper teeth went smoothly without much pain. Plus, the cost was reasonable. I've found my trusted dentist for future checkups. Highly recommend Doctor Praveen Kumar sir for top-notch dental care!
reply_text: Thank you for your valuable feedback.
